  "section": "1.4: 62 farming, Desert Treasure, earth battlestaves",
  "stepText": "Plant willow saplings in at least two places (three for insurance is better. Varrock, Falador and Lumbridge are recommended). Pick a white tree fruit from the white tree for the diary. Games necklace teleport to Burthorpe, visit the Rogues Den and buy 1200 knives (15 bronze, 10 iron, 5 steel) per world from Martin Thwait (optional but not recommended: you can buy about 3x as many so you don’t have to pick them up later, but it’s more world hopping). Exit the Rogues Den and run south and complete Eadgar’s Ruse. Buy 25 water-filled vial packs.\n",
